OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,FThe People's Pension has revealed
OL,7,Fplans to step into private market
OL,8,Finvestment in the months ahead.
OL,10,FThe body is one of the biggest
OL,11,Findependent master trusts in the UK,
OL,12,Fserving more than 6.8 million pension
OL,13,Fsavers and managing #31 billion in
OL,14,Fassets.
OL,16,FIt is set to start investing a
OL,17,Fsignificant proportion into private
OL,18,Fmarkets later this year, with a target
OL,19,Fto grow this allocation to #4 billion
OL,20,Fby 2030, initially in assets such as
OL,21,Finfrastructure and real estate.
