OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,FThe figure is based on projections
OL,7,Faround the total assets under
OL,8,Fmanagement in the years ahead.
OL,10,FA substantial part of the new
OL,11,Fallocation of assets could be deployed
OL,12,Fin the UK, if assets are available
OL,13,Fthat meet the return requirements, the
OL,14,FPeople's Pension said.
