OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,FThe scheme has said its allocation
OL,7,Fwill hinge on it being able to access
OL,8,Fa "dependable pipeline" of good
OL,9,Fquality assets that meet its return
OL,10,Frequirements at a fee level that
OL,11,Fleaves the benefits in the hands of
OL,12,Fmembers, and with the right
OL,13,Foperational structures in place.
OL,15,FThis latest announcement follows the
OL,16,Fscheme's statement last year that it
OL,17,Fhas now reached the scale to deploy
OL,18,Fmeaningfully into private markets.
