OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said:
OL,7,F"Growing the economy is the number one
OL,8,Fmission of the Government.
OL,10,F"This public commitment from one of
OL,11,Fthe UK's largest independent pension
OL,12,Fmaster trusts to invest here, at home
OL,13,Fin Britain, will help drive economic
OL,14,Fgrowth and support our milestone of
OL,15,Fimproving living standards across the
OL,16,FUK."
