OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,FMark Condron, chair of the People's
OL,7,FPension board of trustees, said: "What
OL,8,Fwe are announcing today is a
OL,9,Fsignificant step forward on the path
OL,10,Ftowards the People's Pension investing
OL,11,Fin private markets, including key
OL,12,Fparts of the UK economy.
OL,14,F"We are demonstrating how a
OL,15,Fresponsible asset owner, operating at
OL,16,Fthe right scale, can invest in both
OL,17,Fthe best interests of its members and
OL,18,Fthe benefit of the wider economy in
OL,19,Fwhich they work."
