OL,3,CPeople's Pension plans to invest up to
OL,4,C#4bn into private market assets
OL,6,F"As an independent #31 billion master
OL,7,Ftrust, without shareholders, we
OL,8,Fbelieve that now is the time to
OL,9,Fincrease our investment in private
OL,10,Fassets for the benefit of our savers
OL,11,Fand the growth of the UK economy. The
OL,12,FPeople's Pension has a vital role to
OL,13,Fplay in this exciting plan for the
OL,14,Ffuture of UK retirement savings."
